s = socket.socket(socket.FAMILY, socket.TYPE, socket.PROTOCOL)  #use python to create socket.
socket.socket( *family*, *type*, *proto* ) these three argument are in inside socket class
family: AF_INET*, AF_INET6, AF_UNIX
type: SOCK_STREAM*, SOCK_DGRAM, SOCK_RAW
proto: 0*, IPPROTO_TCP, IPPROTO_UDP, IPPROTO_IP, IPPROTO_ICMP, IPPROTO_RAW
s.setsockopt(socket.SOL_SOCKET, socket.SO_REUSEADDR, 1) #set server socket option
s.bind(('', 12345)) #Bind the Server Listening port to an address:
s.listen() #prepares server for incoming connection
ip_header = pack('!BBHHHBBH4s4s' , ip_ver_ihl, ip_tos, ip_len, ip_id, ip_frag, ip_ttl, ip_proto, ip_check, ip_srcadd, ip_dstadd) #python way of translating all of these sections

ENCODING & DECODING 
Encode text to Hex:
echo "Message" | xxd -p
Encode file to Hex:
xxd file.txt file-encoded.txt
Decode file from Hex:
xxd -r file-encoded.txt file-decoded.txt
